text: Tando Hyder is a town and Union Council of Hyderabad District in the Sindh province of Pakistan. It is part of the rural Taluka of Hyderabad and is located at 25°22'60N 68°25'60E and lies to the east of the capital Hyderabad.Location of Tando Haidar - Falling Rain Genomics ==References== Category:Union councils of Hyderabad District
